long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This chrome extension deletes the cookies for the current domain and reloads the web page. Ideal for debugging your code that uses cookies or for reading newspapers that give you free articles depending on your cookie settings.

Privacy policy:
This extension does not handle any user data.
